|-------------------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------------|
| toolchain         | gcc    | gcc    | gcc    | sdcc   | gcc          |
|-------------------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------------|
| bits              | 8      | 16/32  | 16     | 8      | 32/64        |
|-------------------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------------|
| Sub-Architectures | -      | STM32  | -      | STC    | 1890         |
|                   |        |        |        | AT89   |              |
|-------------------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------------|
| State             | stable | stable | stable | stable | experimental |
|-------------------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------------|


